Package jetbrains.mps.vfs

Class RedispatchListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • jetbrains.mps.vfs.RedispatchListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileEventProcessor, FileListener
    public final class RedispatchListener
extends Object
implements FileListener
    Facility to aggregate multiple file events and process them at once. Utilizes FileSystemEvent.notify(jetbrains.mps.vfs.refresh.FileEventProcessor) mechanism.
    Since:
    2018.3

        Parameters:
        postNotify - delegate for event re-dispatch; FileProcessor uses listener instance as key, make sure you pass same FileEventProcessor instance here if you add multiple instances of RedispatchListener to different files but intend to process their changes in a single listener.
        prefs - preferences of this listener
